  "detailed_description": "Depth of Extinction is a tactical RPG with roguelike elements that features in-depth strategic gameplay and high replay value. <br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/636320/extras/SnapShot.png?t=1523029490\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">GAME FEATURES</h2> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Emergent storyline on randomly generated maps with random encounters<br></li><li> Unlock 11 unique character classes<br></li><li> Outfit your team with more than 150 different weapons, armor, and items<br></li><li> Fight 25 unique enemies from 5 factions<br></li><li> Perma-Death</li></ul><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/636320/extras/world_map_500.png?t=1523029490\" >",
  "about_the_game": "Depth of Extinction is a tactical RPG with roguelike elements that features in-depth strategic gameplay and high replay value. <br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/636320/extras/SnapShot.png?t=1523029490\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">GAME FEATURES</h2> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Emergent storyline on randomly generated maps with random encounters<br></li><li> Unlock 11 unique character classes<br></li><li> Outfit your team with more than 150 different weapons, armor, and items<br></li><li> Fight 25 unique enemies from 5 factions<br></li><li> Perma-Death</li></ul><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/636320/extras/world_map_500.png?t=1523029490\" >",
